; Regression test for issue #663: recursive include detection
;
; Self-inclusion should produce a clear "Recursive include" error rather than
; the misleading "File to include was not found" message.

include 663.test

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 6:
Error: Recursive include of file detected: $FILE
end test
